node.text: Brazilian Popstar @Biel and I talk Facebook and tattoos.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian on August 09, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Woke up to an overwhelming amount of Happy Birthday wishes. I thank you all. If you know me, you know I live in the the moment. Half a lifetime lived, half a lifetime to go. Time is priceless, enjoy it while you got some left.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian on August 03, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, road, street and text that says 'STOP'.

node.text: It’s easy to tell a lie, it’s even easier to believe a lie, but I always say, don’t believe everything you hear, instead, believe everything you see. Stories will be made up about you on your road to success by those who never took the time to understand you for one reason or another. Pay no mind to talkers and focus on your actions cause actions will always speak louder than words.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian on July 10, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: My little ray of sunshine @iamsydneyshea 🧚‍♀️ hard working, talented, and one of the funniest people I know. You’re going places kid! Make sure to check out her music. It’s Fuego!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian in The Moon with @illadaproducer, @weworking, @notemarcato, @scottstorchofficial, @chucktreece, and @_xavierdaniel. May be an image of 3 people, people sitting, people standing and indoor.

node.text: We only do legendary things around these here parts. Legendary I tell ya.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian on June 20, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people standing, footwear and sky.

node.text: I used to share my ideas with people who 100% of the time would end up stealing them in one way or another and benefit from them leaving me behind. When I started keeping things to myself, I saw quickly that my progress was moving along a lot faster. As a creator, I wanted to create a company that catered to the creators and not the investors. Everyone is so caught up trying to please the money guys instead of focusing on putting the creators first. @thevibez is for the creators by a creator. I’ve partnered with some talented people and friends of mine to make this all possible. It’s just getting started.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian on June 09, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and footwear.

node.text: I’m in sweats 90% of the time. I choose comfort over anything else.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian on June 07, 2021. May be an image of pool.

node.text: A VIBE.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian in Beverly Hills, California with @brandonluau, and @unicornexotics. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Smell is the closest thing we have to a time machine. Nothing revives the past so completely as a smell that was once associated with it.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian on May 30, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: Vibez LA was fun. Miami next...

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian in Los Angeles, California with @notemarcato. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Just before the beat drops...

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian on April 17, 2021. May be an image of one or more people.

node.text: I can’t wait for tour season to fully begin. There’s nothing more fun than being on the road putting on a show night after night. It’s been sooo long 😫

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pierre Balian on March 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: God is good. 🙏🏼
